## Usage

### Reading progress bar (zero JS)

```html
<link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css" />

<div class="em-progress-bar em-scroll-timeline em-progress-fill"></div>
```

### Fade-in on scroll

```html
<div class="em-scroll-view em-fade-up">
  I fade in from below as I enter the viewport.
</div>
```

### Staggered cards

```html
<div class="cards-grid stagger">
  <div class="card em-scroll-view em-fade-up">Card 1</div>
  <div class="card em-scroll-view em-fade-up">Card 2</div>
  <div class="card em-scroll-view em-fade-up">Card 3</div>
</div>
```

### Clip-path text reveal

```html
<h2 class="em-scroll-view em-reveal-clip">Revealed as you scroll</h2>
```

