## All Utility Classes

### Animation triggers (timeline binding)

| Class | Effect |
|---|---|
| `.em-scroll-view` | Binds to `view()` — fires as element enters viewport |
| `.em-scroll-timeline` | Binds to `scroll(root)` — tracks page scroll position |

### Animation effects (pair with `.em-scroll-view`)

| Class | Effect |
|---|---|
| `.em-fade-in` | Simple opacity fade |
| `.em-fade-up` | Fade + rise from below |
| `.em-fade-down` | Fade + drop from above |
| `.em-fade-left` | Fade + slide from right |
| `.em-fade-right` | Fade + slide from left |
| `.em-scale-up` | Fade + grow into place |
| `.em-scale-down` | Fade + shrink into place |
| `.em-rotate-in` | Fade + slight rotation |
| `.em-flip-x` | 3D horizontal flip entrance |
| `.em-flip-y` | 3D vertical flip entrance |
| `.em-blur-in` | Blur-to-focus entrance |
| `.em-reveal-clip` | Horizontal clip-path sweep |

### Scroll-timeline effects (pair with `.em-scroll-timeline`)

| Class | Effect |
|---|---|
| `.em-progress-fill` | Animates `width` from `0%` to `100%` |
| `.em-parallax-slow` | Slow vertical parallax shift |

### Component

| Class | Description |
|---|---|
| `.em-progress-bar` | Fixed reading-progress bar (positioned, styled, gradient) |

### Delay modifiers

`.em-delay-100` / `.em-delay-200` / `.em-delay-300` / `.em-delay-400` / `.em-delay-500`

