## Browser Support

| Browser | Scroll-Driven Animations | Fallback |
|---|---|---|
| Chrome 115+ | ✅ Full support | — |
| Edge 115+ | ✅ Full support | — |
| Opera 101+ | ✅ Full support | — |
| Firefox | ❌ (flag behind pref) | Animations play immediately on load |
| Safari | ❌ Not yet supported | Animations play immediately on load |

Fallback is handled via `@supports (animation-timeline: view())` — unsupported browsers always see content, it just appears without scroll-driven motion.

---

## Accessibility

All scroll-driven animations are automatically disabled when the user has `prefers-reduced-motion: reduce` set in their OS. Elements become immediately visible with no transform or opacity change.

