## CSS Custom Properties

Override these on `:root` or any parent element:

```css
:root {
  --em-accent:       #6c63ff;   /* Primary accent colour */
  --em-accent-2:     #ff6584;   /* Secondary accent (used in progress bar gradient) */
  --em-scroll-easing: linear;   /* Easing for scroll-view animations */
  --em-scroll-fill:   both;     /* animation-fill-mode */
}
```

